696
00:54:59,139 --> 00:55:00,309
Tenanglah, Ye Na.

697
00:55:00,539 --> 00:55:01,710
"Ye Na"?

698
00:55:04,819 --> 00:55:05,980
Lepas cincin itu.

699
00:55:07,920 --> 00:55:09,149
Lepas.

700
00:55:09,950 --> 00:55:11,660
Manajer Tim Seo, kau ini kenapa.

701
00:55:11,660 --> 00:55:12,789
Lepas, kubilang.

702
00:55:20,030 --> 00:55:21,599
Oppa pasti akan segera siuman.

703
00:55:21,899 --> 00:55:23,170
